Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is far enough.\NDo not touch Her Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Andalusia Leader to all units.\NTarget the transport only.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if they launch Kataphrakts,\Ndo not engage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will use Kaufmann 6 as an anchor\Nto perform wire swingby{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and return to Trident Base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good hunting, people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Target located.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All units, commence attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind's too strong...\NOur rounds are drifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm! They're in\Nthe same boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hit 'em before they can get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple high-density satellites!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hit them at this range!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back on the bullets! Keep firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Andalusia 33, I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damage minor! Continuing missi–
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Andalusia 33!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Andalusia 22!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can he land any shots in this wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Intense thermal reading approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Tharsis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please get clear. I'll handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Slaine Troyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Andalusia 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hitting... I'm this close,\Nso how can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The blessings of my lady, Princess\NRoyal Asseylum, are upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was young,\NI idolized Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its blue seas. Its blue skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That world has the privilege of\Nwater and air and sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and is blessed with an abundance\Nof life and natural resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I once lost my life\Non that world of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, my eyes were\Nopened to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How outrageous it was for the Terrans
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to live among that bounty\Nwithout appreciating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A foolish race that covets\Nresources, destroys nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and is devoted to the\Npursuit of pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't allow them to have their way\Nwith this precious world of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:04:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Asseylum Vers Allusia,\NPrincess Royal of the Vers Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,praise and commend all those\NOrbital Knights who have died
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the name of that noble cause.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of watching that\Npirate broadcast of theirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious, that's all... I wonder\Nwhat happened to the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was\Non Earth's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she lost hope in there ever\Nbeing a peaceful resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's fighting, it's only natural\Nthat she would side with Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Martian, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Inko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Inko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing. I was just thinking that\Nthis might be our last chance to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we board the ship tomorrow\Nand lift off the day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's not him\Nyou're thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there, people!\NAre you training or aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We plan to be able to lift off\Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Troops whose arrival was delayed\Nshould be here by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the top\Nbrass are thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll essentially be going into\Nbattle with our vitals exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If those vitals are competent\Nenough, it changes things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're telling us to put it\Nto effective use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe we'll be fighting\Nside by side again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle he made it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That landing was so skillful, one would never\Nguess we are in an uneven gravity field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills have improved\Neven more, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your compliment honors me,\NCount Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Granting you the title of knight\Nwas a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did the battle go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I destroyed some four\Nenemy units.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a coup, Milord Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Mr. Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for\N"milord" with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do, Milord.\NI am your manservant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're older than I am, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Terran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That does not change the fact\Nthat you are a knight, Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I ask that you refrain from using\N"mister" with me, Milord Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in good spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am weary, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How fares the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The invasions of North and\NSouth America are complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and their takeover is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for Eurasia and the Far East,\NUEF counterattacks continue
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,due to the surrender of the\NLanding Castles there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to\Ngo down to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We expect the UE\Nto be exhausted soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, you,\Nwho inherit the bloodline
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of the Emperor of Vers,\Nwill be installed as–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have never been pleased with\Nthe blood flowing in my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, I find it repugnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I only being kept alive\Nbecause of the value of my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To merely be a tool that\Nexists to awaken Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who extended the hand of\Nfriendship to me, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I curse my blood,\NI am grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Highness. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you teach me of Earth again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're together\Nagain for a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we make it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat the Martians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat them and restore\Npeace on Earth. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise attack!\NIt's a Martian Kataphrakt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Radar return confirmed, south-southwest,\N20 klicks. Closing at 50kph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to battle stations.\NWe're leaving the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the antigravity device\Nis being serviced!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the uniform you\Nwere supplied with?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it wasn't very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't–
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. It won't hinder her ability to\Nhelm the ship, so I'll authorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki, shall I tell you\Nwhy you can't get a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deucalion, activate! Kataphrakt squadron,\Nlaunch all operational units!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any enemy intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Yacoym's Kataphrakt, Frozen Elysium.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its Aldnoah Drive's unique capability\Nis Entropy Dilution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entro-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It saps the molecular motion of all matter\Ninside a field 1km in radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It creates super-low temperatures that can\Ntransform the air and freeze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Terrans. show me how\Nyou defy the power of Aldnoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At its current rate of speed, it'll reach\Nthe Deucalion's dock in 15 minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to slow it\Ndown somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Slow it down?\NYou must be joking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Harbinger Platoon. Target spotted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in\Nin cold-weather mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turbine output to maximum. De-icers, on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The de-icers aren't working? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are helpless before it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not for nothing that\Nits name is Frozen Elysium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voltage is falling? The chemical reaction\Nin my batteries has stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbinger Leader!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My rounds aren't connecting! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A shield? It shouldn't have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of options!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad. We have to think\Nof a way to slow it down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said we were\Ngoing to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Call it a downward revision!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Measuring bullet trajectory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. The warheads entered\Na superconductive state
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and were deflected by\Nthe Meissner Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how air burst mode works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A dud? Oh, the battery in the warhead\Nfroze and the processor locked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where does the sapped heat go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it shunting the molecular movement\Nenergy somewhere else in our dimension?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flight distance for the warheads'\Nelectronic timer fuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about 50 meters should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Radius of the field, 1km...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20 rounds should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inaho?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charging enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll freeze!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to reach him\Nbefore then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How amusing. Come, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grenade launcher, midair burst mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe distance, cut. Flight distance, 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I took more damage than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Calm will be mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Inaho Kaizuka reporting.\NPer orders from General Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been assigned to your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's with that?\NYou never change, Inaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back at you, Inko.\NI'm glad you're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have changed. Quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can make polite small talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back...\NWelcome back, Inaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have finished off the Terran soldier\Nwho has been a thorn in our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have finally made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me for all the wrongs\NI have done you in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and am sure to do\Nin the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many Terran troops have already\Nbreached the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape in the Tharsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And take Princess Asseylum with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only one who can\Nsave you now, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you die with your\Nambitions unrealized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or choose to live with\NPrincess Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your decision, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho! Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki! Inaho's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Yagarai! You have\Nto do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gunshot wound to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet went through the temporal\Nregion via the left eye socket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Patient unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three cc's of adrenaline administered\Nas emergency treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll save him, right?\NYou'll save Inaho, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He needs immediate\Nsurgical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And a transfusion, of course. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have tools and facilities\Nin the underground shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Capt. Magbaredge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Order the Deucalion to lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Aldnoah Drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Kaizuka...\NPrincess Asseylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.07,Egg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not his...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's blood splatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The light of Aldnoah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The activation factor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deucalion, lift off!\NAll ahead, dead slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ahead, dead slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the atmosphere.\NNow coasting on inertia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Course, Trident Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Electromagnetic grid, fire.\NMonitor all wavelengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Terrans who so foolishly squandered\Nthe goodwill of the Vers Empire{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are even now biding their time to attempt\Nto steal our lands from us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Vers Empire must exterminate them out of mercy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fighting her. Is that okay, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We shall take the blue Earth for Vers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us liberate this world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which possesses air and water\Nin such quantities that it diffracts light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and makes the sky and seas appear blue,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from the hands of the barbaric Terrans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rayleigh scattering that makes the sky blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water, please, Eddelrittuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Milady! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was that, Count Saazbaum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. You were the very\Nimage of Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one would ever suspect\Nyour true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the problem with you men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one was speaking\Nof true identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Masterfully done, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your majestic words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are sure to have left an impression\Non the Orbital Knights, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sir Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am more grateful for such concern than\Nany compliments on my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am extremely and humbly delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there will be nothing else, Milord Slaine,\NI will take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've returned, Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you are in good\Nspirits again today.
